from\": 337, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"his maiden Olympic stint\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I should focus on myself and let the other gymnasts do what they do,\\\" said Yulo in a mix of Filipino and English when asked about the lessons he picked up from his Tokyo Games run.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396836170883609e-52, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other gymnasts\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"a mix\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"the lessons\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"his Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all worked hard and we all worked ourselves to exhaustion in training.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I should focus on where I am at and be confident of my moves,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my moves\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I should not get carried away by my mood and I should trust what I practiced.\\\"\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mood\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then 21 years old, Yulo competed in Tokyo as a legitimate medal contender, having won bronze and gold in floor exercise in the 2018 and 2019 editions of the World Artistic Gymnastics Championships, respectively.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9